TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(PRD.QTR_PERIOD_BEGIN_DT) AS QTR_PERIOD_BEGIN_DT ,MAX(PRD.QTR_PERIOD_END_DT) AS QTR_PERIOD_END_DT ,MAX(BCI.DSPN_DT) AS DSPN_DT ,MAX(BCI.RBAT_ID) AS RBAT_ID ,MAX(BCI.EXTL_SRC_CD) AS EXTL_SRC_CD ,MAX(BCI.EXTL_LVL1_ID) AS EXTL_LVL1_ID ,MAX(BCI.EXTL_LVL2_ID) AS EXTL_LVL2_ID ,MAX(BCI.EXTL_LVL3_ID) AS EXTL_LVL3_ID ,SUM(RCN.BASE_DISC_APC_AMT) AS BASE_DISCNT_AMT ,SUM(RCN.PERF_DISC_APC_AMT) AS PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT ,SUM(RCN.CTRC_DISC_APC_AMT) AS CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT ,SUM(RCN.FRMLY_DISC_APC_AMT) AS FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT ,SUM(RCN.PRC_PTCT_DISC_APC_AMT ) AS PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT ,SUM(RCN.ADMN_DISC_APC_AMT) AS ADMN_DISCNT_AMT ,MAX(BCI.IC_AMT) AS IC_AMT ,MAX(BCA.CTRC_FEE_PD_AMT) AS CTRC_FEE_PD_AMT ,MAX(BCA.TAX_AMT) AS TAX_AMT ,MAX(BCI.MBR_RBAT_DISC_AMT) AS MBR_RBAT_DISC_AMT ,MAX(BCA.INSRD_ID) AS INSRD_ID ,BCI.CLM_GID ,SUM( RCN.ADMN_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS ADMN_DISC_DSADJ_AMT ,SUM( RCN.BASE_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS BASE_DISC_DSADJ_AMT ,SUM( RCN.PERF_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS PERF_DISC_DSADJ_AMT ,SUM( RCN.FRMLY_DISC_DSADJ_AMT ) AS FRMLY_DISC_DSADJ_AMT ,SUM( RCN.CTRC_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS CTRC_DISC_DSADJ_AMT ,SUM(RCN.PRC_PTCT_DSADJ_DISC_AMT) AS PRC_PTCT_DSADJ_DISC_AMT ,MAX(PRD.PERIOD_PARENT_ID) AS PERIOD_PARENT_ID --Added the below columns as part of PRF 1713 Aetna Invoice Extract Additions ,BCI.CLM_LVL1_ID AS CLM_LVL1_ID ,BCI.CLM_LVL2_ID AS CLM_LVL2_ID ,BCI.CLM_TYP_CD AS CLM_TYP_CD ,BCI.MED_PYBL_CD AS MED_PYBL_CD ,BCI.AP_CO_CD AS AP_CO_CD FROM vrap.TDISCNT_PERIOD PD ,VRAP.rcnt_dex_cntl DEX , vrap.RCNT_RECN_HDR HDR , vrap.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM RCN , vrap.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS PRD , vrap.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV BCI , vrap.RCIT_BASE_CLM_APC BCA WHERE PD.QUARTER_ID=DEX.obj_gid AND DEX.DEX_GID=$$TXN_GID and PD.PERIOD_ID = HDR.RBAT_RPT_PRD_ID and HDR.RECN_STAT_CD in (3,4,9) and HDR.RECN_GID in (select distinct RECN_GID from vrap.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR x, VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_DTL y where x.INV_ID=y.INV_ID and y.MODEL_TYP_CD='T') and HDR.RECN_GID = RCN.RECN_GID and RCN.RECN_SCRB_CD in (0,1) and PRD.QUARTER_ID=DEX.obj_gid and PRD.MODEL_TYP_CD='T' and PRD.MODEL_TYP_CD = BCI.MODEL_TYP_CD and PRD.MNTH_PERIOD_END_DT = BCI.INV_ELIG_DT and RCN.CLM_GID = BCI.CLM_GID and BCI.CLM_GID=BCA.CLM_GID GROUP BY BCI.CLM_GID, BCI.CLM_LVL1_ID, BCI.CLM_LVL2_ID, BCI.CLM_TYP_CD, BCI.MED_PYBL_CD, BCI.AP_CO_CD WITH UR

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION:
Added to evaluate detail file fields.
For Alpha Numeric Fields: Should be left-justified and then space-filled. If no value is provided for a given field, the field should be space-filled.
For Numeric Fields: Should be right-justified and left zero-padded to the length of the field. E.g. a six digit negative 99.95 would be represented as '?09995'. a positive 99.95 would be represented as '+09995' or '009995', since use of the positive sign is optional. If no value is provided for a given field, the field should be zero filled ('000000?).
INSTANCE.NAME: Exp_Evaluate_Detail_Fields
